        <img src="home-icon.png" alt="Head back home">
    </a>  
</div>
<div class="about-page-wrapper">
    <h1> What is <%= quizName %>!</h1>
    
    <p>Welcome to <strong><%= quizName %></strong>, your new favorite math playground! 🚀 Whether you're a number ninja 🥷, a subtraction superstar, or a geometry guru, we've got something for everyone. Our interactive quizzes bring the thrill of problem-solving to life while making sure you have fun along the way.</p>
    
    <p>Here at <%= quizName %>, we believe that learning should be as exciting as solving a mystery — but way more rewarding. So, why not level up your math skills and embark on a journey to become a Math Whiz? 🌟</p>
    
    <p>Our quizzes are designed for all ages and skill levels, so whether you're starting from scratch or you're already a math maestro, we've got the challenges to keep you on your toes.</p>

    <h2>Why <%= quizName %>? 🤔</h2>
    
    <ul>
        <li><strong>Interactive & Fun:</strong> Quizzes that make math feel like play, not work.</li>
        <li><strong>Level Up:</strong> Progress through levels as you master new concepts.</li>
        <li><strong>For Everyone:</strong> From kids to adults, whether you’re solving your first addition problem or gearing up for Algebra, we've got you covered.</li>
        <li><strong>Instant Feedback:</strong> Get real-time results and track your progress to see how much you've learned.</li>
    </ul>

    <p>At <%= quizName %>, we're on a mission to prove that math isn't just numbers and formulas — it's a language of logic that unlocks the secrets of the universe. And hey, it’s fun, too! 💡</p>

    <p>So grab your virtual pencil ✏️, put on your thinking cap 🧢, and let's get started — your math adventure begins now!</p>
</div>
